<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about">
    <h2>About Nishpaksh Samajh</h2>
    <p>
        Nishpaksh Samajh rejects mental hierarchy, competitive ego-systems, and manipulative ideologies.  
        It promotes <strong>neutral consciousness, equality, and universal coexistence with nature</strong>.
    </p>
    <p><strong>Core Mission:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Free the human mind from jealousy, comparison, and dominance</li>
        <li>Reconnect humanity with nature — as a living parent</li>
        <li>Promote equality among all beings</li>
        <li>Build a future (Yatharth Yug) where love, compassion, and unbiased awareness prevail</li>
    </ul>
</section>

